The Ministry of Health together with the concerned ministries and agencies supported by the European Regional Office of WHO has developed a draft Action Plan for Prevention and Control of NCDs for 2014-2020 . The draft document includes amendments and additions to the legal documents for the following:
( a) placing a ban on display of tobacco products . the shelves of trade and catering ;
(b ) prohibit the implementation of any product (eg . candy . toys. trinkets . etc.) in the form of alcoholic beverages and tobacco products;
 ( c) the prohibition of ingredients that stimulate the use of tobacco products .
